A_552 - Sometimes for people, based on the work done by their parents, it can be difficult to carry out particular reasoning. In particular, for children to improve their diet by choosing healthier foods, when you are at home it is more tiring in terms of decision-making if a parent cooks. Children generally always prefer the tastiest foods over the healthier but more challenging ones to eat, because they cannot imagine what is &ldquo;on the other side of the fence&rdquo;...